                        <h1 class="u-mb-l u-fs-xxl">What if I’m away or abroad on Census Day?</h1>

                        <div class="page__body">

                            <p>Census Day is Sunday 21 March 2021.</p>

                            <p>If there's someone staying or living in your home and they're filling in the household form, they should include you there.</p>

                            <p>If there's no one at home, please fill it in as soon as you get back. You can also use your access code to complete online while you're away.</p>

                            <p>If you’re away from the UK on this date, for less than 12 months, you should still be counted in the census.</p>

